                                <entry>
<para>to set and any other options such as to screen etc </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                    </table>
                </formalpara>
                <formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>$this if any params passed, current level if not  </para>
</formalpara>
